				<td colspan="2"><span>Greetings fellow bards <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-10.gif" border="0" alt="Blushing" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
I have been a (mostly) long term lurker on these boards, and I so much appreciate what I have learned from my fellow 'band members'  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
Background: Banerian is my 1st/primary/most fun toon, and he just Ding'ed 60 a few nights ago. My current magelo is here: <a target="_new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=912888">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=912888</a>. 
<br />

<br />
What I'm hoping for are suggestions for what to focus on next. I have a couple of potential paths, but would very much like to hear from others with a bit more experience<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
1. I'm 2 drops away from epic: guts from Eldrig the Old and this small 'date' with Trakanon ... think I can get a group of 'capable friends' together that should be enough to fight the dragon *crosses fingers* ... and I have to admit: I really want to be part of an honest to goodness dragon fight (Yeah, bought my scales <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-10.gif" border="0" alt="Blushing" hspace="2" />).
<br />

<br />
2. Brewing is at 248. Tried once (with Geerlock) for the GM Trophy and failed ... but willing to try again. Stats are nice ...
<br />

<br />
3. OK with grinding XP to level if that is a recommendation.
<br />

<br />
4. What else? Solo/Duo (50-ish shammy or 58 Cleric) camps for &quot;good stuff&quot;?
<br />

<br />
Ohh. Not in a raiding guild, but that might change (getting a bit tired of chatting in guild with my trader as the only other one on <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-9.gif" border="0" alt="Crying" hspace="2" />)
<br />

<br />
Money/Plat: willing to farm if Baz buys are recommended...
<br />

<br />
Any suggestion/advice/help/etc. will be much appreciated!!
<br />

<br />
Banerian, proud lvl 60 (atm) BARD on Stromm
<br />

<br />
--------
<br />

<br />
EDIT/UPDATE: Went Baz shopping based on suggestions, so Magelo is updated. More extensive post below.</span></td>
