				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Yeah I know: another &amp;quot;how is my gear&amp;quot; post (lvl 60 now) :-)<a name="70794"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 9 04 1:48 AM</span></td>
