				<td colspan="2"><span>Well, how much cash are you willing to make/spend?  Couple hundred thousand plat or less would probably add a good 1000 hp/mana to your gear.  Sounds like a lot, but I know warriors that spend more than that on a BoC.  The new OoW tradables are really nice, and you can get some good deals on them.  All my gear with the exception of the epic and vots were bazaar bought.
<br />

<br />
You're getting close to the point (with fade) where mana is going to be an issue.  So don't neglect that totally in favor of hps.  Look for mana and FT also if possible.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
