				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Yeah I know: another &amp;amp;quot;how is my gear&amp;amp;quot; post (lvl 60 now) :-)<a name="70805"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 9 04 10:45 AM</span></td>
